from manim import *

class RoundedRectangleExample(Scene):
    def construct(self):
        rect_1 = RoundedRectangle(corner_radius=0.5)
        rect_2 = RoundedRectangle(corner_radius=1.5, height=4.0, width=4.0)

        rect_group = Group(rect_1, rect_2).arrange(buff=1)
        self.add(rect_group)
